@startuml VibeCodium - Sequence (Vercel Deploy)
title VibeCodium - Deploy to Vercel

actor User
participant "VibeCodium\nApp" as Client
participant "Backend" as Server
participant "GitHub" as GitHub
participant "Vercel" as Vercel

User -> Client : Click "Deploy"

alt Missing API tokens
  Client -> User : Redirect to Profile — add tokens
end

Client -> Server : Deploy project
Server -> GitHub : Create repository & push code
GitHub --> Server : Repository ready

Server -> Vercel : Trigger deployment
Vercel --> Server : Build in progress...

loop Waiting for build
  Server -> Vercel : Check status
  Vercel --> Server : Still building...
end

Vercel --> Server : Deployment ready\n(live URL)
Server --> Client : Share live URL
Client -> User : Open app in new tab

@enduml
